OL,3,CSNP secure win but Reform poised to
OL,4,Cdisrupt status quo of Scottish politics
OL,6,FThe SNP have secured a fifth
OL,7,Fconsecutive win at Holyrood, and for
OL,8,Fthe second time in just over a week,
OL,9,Ftheir leader has received a message
OL,10,Ffrom the Oval Office.
OL,12,FDonald Trump has congratulated John
OL,13,FSwinney on his social media on his
OL,14,F"Big Election Victory".
OL,16,FDespite the party falling short of the
OL,17,F65-seat majority they sought to
OL,18,Fachieve, they will be the largest
OL,19,Fparty at Holyrood with Swinney on
OL,20,Fcourse to be reappointed as First
OL,21,FMinister.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@VO]
