OL,3,CSNP secure win but Reform poised to
OL,4,Cdisrupt status quo of Scottish politics
OL,6,FHere comes the fun part - the
OL,7,Fnegotiation to see who will prop up
OL,8,Fhim up.
OL,10,FHe will now be looking to the Scottish
OL,11,FGreens to give him a majority to
OL,12,Fsecure a pro-independence government
OL,13,Fin Holyrood. They're on a high after
OL,14,Fsweeping up 15 seats, mainly for the
OL,15,Fregional list vote.
OL,17,FTheir previous power-sharing
OL,18,Farrangement didn't end well, with the
OL,19,FBute House Agreement torn up before
OL,20,FSwinney took the helm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
