OL,3,CSNP secure win but Reform poised to
OL,4,Cdisrupt status quo of Scottish politics
OL,6,FBut watch out for the new kids on the
OL,7,Fblock who are ready to disrupt the
OL,8,Fstatus quo of Scottish politics.
OL,10,FReform, which only had one MSP before
OL,11,Fthis election, will now enter the
OL,12,Fchamber with 17 - tied with Scottish
OL,13,FLabour.
OL,15,FThe second-place party in Holyrood
OL,16,Ftraditionally leads the opening cross
OL,17,Fat First Ministers' Questions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
