OL,3,CSNP secure win but Reform poised to
OL,4,Cdisrupt status quo of Scottish politics
OL,6,FUnlike Westminster, there isn't an
OL,7,Fofficial opposition party at Holyrood.
OL,8,FWill Labour and Reform agree to take
OL,9,Fit in turns at FMQs?
OL,11,FI doubt it.
OL,13,FReform failed to secure any
OL,14,Fconstituency seats, narrowly missing
OL,15,Fout to the SNP by 346 votes in
OL,16,FBanffshire and Buchan Coast.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
