OL,3,CSNP secure win but Reform poised to
OL,4,Cdisrupt status quo of Scottish politics
OL,6,FLeader Malcolm Offord had publicly
OL,7,Fstated he expected to win 20-25 seats
OL,8,Fbut fell short of his own expectations.
OL,10,FReform has divided the unionist vote
OL,11,Fin Scotland, undoubtedly benefiting
OL,12,Fthe SNP.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, Scottish Labour has gone
OL,15,Funderground after their worst
OL,16,Fperformance in Scottish Election
OL,17,Fhistory.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
