OL,3,CSNP secure win but Reform poised to
OL,4,Cdisrupt status quo of Scottish politics
OL,6,FLeader Anas Sarwar declared defeat
OL,7,Fwhen he arrived at his count in
OL,8,FGlasgow, a far cry from his triumphant
OL,9,Fentrance there during the general
OL,10,Felection sweep in 2024. Many of the
OL,11,Fresults hadn't even been declared.
OL,13,FWhile the party lick their wounds,
OL,14,Fthey place the blame at the door of
OL,15,FNumber 10 Downing Street.
OL,17,FSarwar's attempts to distance himself
OL,18,Ffrom Prime Minister Keir Starmer's
OL,19,Fweren't enough to convince voters he
OL,20,Fcould deliver the change he promised.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
