OL,3,CSNP secure win but Reform poised to
OL,4,Cdisrupt status quo of Scottish politics
OL,6,FThe Scottish Conservatives have fallen
OL,7,Faway, returning with 12 MSPs, down on
OL,8,Fthe last vote while the Scottish
OL,9,FLiberal Democrats seeing their total
OL,10,Fincrease to 10.
OL,12,FThe corridors of Holyrood are set to
OL,13,Fwelcome a host of fresh and familiar
OL,14,Ffaces, and they certainly have a lot
OL,15,Fto get on with.
OL,17,FA flatlining health service, a
OL,18,Fstruggling economy, and island
OL,19,Fcommunities crying out for lifeline
OL,20,Fferries that are over budget and
OL,21,Fdelayed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
